{"tid":1743723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"轉推：記者有話說","createTime":"2019-11-21T10:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T12:21:52.000Z","uid":44822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0a560393391f8c3c4b1200f685d69934d61eb70","tid":1743723,"uid":44822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"【採訪手記：記者不是Condom】<br />\n<br />\n我一向都好隨和，平時你叫我唔好影，我咪唔影囉。<br />\n<br />\n但係去到有啲大件事時刻，好似人踩人事件咁，我第一時間衝去影相，有個FA第一時間遮我鏡頭，叫我「咪撚影」。我都唔知佢用乜理由阻我紀錄，我真係拍攝人踩人的慘況，紀錄真相。<br />\n<br />\n當晚，有另一班FA經蘋果日報問我，「有冇影到相啊？」<br />\n<br />\n心諗，想點？一個又叫我唔好影，一個又問我有冇影到相，要認樣。<br />\n<br />\n嗱正如FA要救警察、救藍絲、救林鄭，我都唔會阻止。同樣你哋都唔好一個阻我影相，阻完另一個又要問我拎相，Am I a joke to you?<br />\n<br />\n編按：時移世易，傳媒處理新聞的方法也有所改變，比如從前被捕者須要打格遮樣，現在反而要被捕人的樣子清晰可見。當然，更重要的是新聞自由，記者在前線紀錄真相，市民才可以從多方面資訊去了解事情，貼近事實。正如不久之前，人踩人事件彷彿是個都市流言一樣。<br />\n<br />\n文 / Kaiser @ USP United Social Press社媒<br />\n攝 / Jimmy Lam @ USP United Social Press社媒"},{"pid":"a8933b0bac16b63a8fb47b6f1eabcbf95a904b46","tid":1743723,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T10:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">入黎望望</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【極重要】香港前途 - 終局分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743693</a>"},{"pid":"88edbb5909d1b83a9673988eabaff7abe7ee6a87","tid":1743723,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742018</a>"},{"pid":"29d33ca91e4f52bbd113bfa01ca5668626d2d177","tid":1743723,"uid":44822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5518b7b02ca05011abbc25a41dfe0f063eba7322","tid":1743723,"uid":44822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:07:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5940e2aafef800bc609308e13a83691f2295ce36","tid":1743723,"uid":44822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}